      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Outmoded now. These formatting codes are now supplanted by the formatting codes of the <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/time/format/DateTimeFormatter.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>DateTimeFormatter</code></a> class, per JSR 310."
