    "body" : "<pre><code>SimpleDateFormat sdf = new SimpleDateFormat(&quot;hh:mm:ss a&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>(&quot;hh:mm:ss a&quot;) &gt;&gt;&gt; Here if we don't use 'a' then 24hours will be appeared. so if we want to AM/PM in your time just add this format. if any confusion please let me know.</p>\n"
  }, {
