      "body" : "In 2019 please don’t teach the young ones to use the long outdated and notoriously troublesome <code>SimpleDateFormat</code> class. At least not as the first option. And not without any reservation. Today we have so much better in <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/datetime/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>java.time</code>, the modern Java date and time API</a> and its <code>DateTimeFormatter</code>."
