      "body" : "I probably could not disagree more, @BhavikMehta. I do not expect <code>SimpleDateFormat</code> to stay in all future Java versions, at least not without deprecation. The value of keeping code compatible with Java 1.4 is non-existing. And keeping hard-to-maintain code -- certainly is not the best thing in the world."
